  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5300988/" class="title-link">经验的模糊性</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5300988"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36256873/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36256873-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36256873/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">zmcyber</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-11"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-11 00:45:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5300988_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不知道为什么译成“经验的疆界”？不过，译者的翻译水平还是很高的，称赞！  读马奇的书使我感到渺小：人其实是很偶然地出现在这个世界上的，和未知相比，已知的还太少。  读马奇的书使我感到激情：事物是可以不用按照成败与否来认识的，平凡中可以孕育意外，而意外中蕴含新生...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
